{"tid":2233973,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"樓上新租客好嘈，點對付","createTime":"2020-10-07T13:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T17:34:21.000Z","uid":307720,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0f664fdfce3146a47f2927e5f6e0d227302a22bd","tid":2233973,"uid":307720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n樓上個租客9月頭搬過嚟，<br />\n我以往住左十幾年都好清靜，<br />\n直到有晚十二點一點，樓上係咁搬野，又有啲波子聲，完全訓唔到。<br />\n去到第二晚都係咁，咁唯有即刻上去同佢反映下啦。<br />\n佢同我話琴日係第一日搬入黎，咁我體諒。<br />\n<br />\nok，去到9月尾夜晚十點幾，樓上開p咁嘅款，玩到個地板啪啪聲，不停拖台（對依啲聲好敏感）。<br />\n所以我又上去同佢投訴：可唔可以靜小小啊？你晚晚都咁樣拖台，下面好食聲㗎。<br />\n然後佢就話有小朋友生日。心諗大哂？你唔識教？<br />\n<br />\n其實佢每晚九、十、十一點先黎搬野、拖台拖到卡卡聲，依家又係咁，仲要係斷斷續續咁，真心可以點解決？頭兩次上去都好聲好氣提佢。<br />\n租屋租到咁好撚缺德，完全唔諗樓下感受。住左係到十幾年，以前樓上都唔會咁，夜晚安安靜靜。係條仆街租客嚟咗之後影響哂生活質素，上面一有動靜就燥到仆<br />\n好嬲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7918c7920a43cf51f9f39bcd1758902b0862d52c","tid":2233973,"uid":98473,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"標準答案<br />\n震樓神器"},{"pid":"175916dd3e546e138812c6876ebfce5308447eb9","tid":2233973,"uid":356254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓豬 樓下先有優勢"},{"pid":"11552a5f8ff84adc24baaaa5bc43a3087648faee","tid":2233973,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f664fdfce3146a47f2927e5f6e0d227302a22bd","tid":2233973,"uid":307720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2